    "To ensure comprehensive coverage across various medical domains, a stratified sampling method was adopted for paper selection from almost all affiliated medical schools and departments of a university.",
    "We employed multiple evaluators, repetitive trials, and experiments on prompt engineering strategies to enhance the integrity of results.",
    "Our findings demonstrated that GPTs can effectively extract or summarize information described in the abstracts.",
    "Notably, GPT-4.0 exhibits robust performance in providing thorough answers and understanding and summarizing abstracts.",
    "However, there is still room for improvement in accurately discerning information that requires sophisticated understanding and domain expertise."
